Strangely enough, there is an "Ultimate Collection" of Bob Dylan that you can buy at the stores, but there appears to be no such record as "The Ultimate Best Of" Bob Dylan. The "folder.jpg" included within the torrent is *not* the cover of any CD. The torrent contains some duplicate songs. In a few words, this is a composition by a fan, disguised (by the title) as a product. I'd be willing to bet that it is as remastered as I am albino.
